The `eval-stdin.php` file, when exposed, allows external access to this URI, making systems with an exposed `/vendor` folder particularly vulnerable. This vulnerability has been widely exploited in the wild, with observed attack attempts numbering in the millions. The fix for this issue involves updating PHPUnit to a patched version or ensuring that the PHPUnit module is not exposed to external HTTP requests."""
